title: Below Deck: Having a God Moment
description: This week on Below Deck Mediterranean, a whole bunch of stuff almost goes wrong... but it doesn't. A beach picnic, a dinner for Sandy, a jet ski incident — they all go off without a hitch. So there's that. And Matt still drives us mad.
author: watchwhatcrappens@gmail.com (benron)
